Dialogue:
You must clear your
mind and become one
with the blade.
Not now. Eating dango.
I believe I could fly...
I'm drunk!? YOU'RE drunk!

...And then she stormed
out saying she was joining
the Sekiseigumi!

Rhalgr take yer sticks!
Me hands'll do me fine.

These 'ere sticks make
fer good shovels, like.

That was the most
amazing play I've seen!
...Well, this week at least.

I will need to see what
is in this crate and these
barrels before <If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),12))><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),4))>sunrise<Else/>midday</If><Else/><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),17))>sundown<Else/>sunrise</If></If>.

A thousand apologies.
Your skiff will be here
at any moment.
Sound the alarm!
You will not escape us!

Make yourselves at
home, honored travelers.

Come on. It's my turn
to play with the stick.

Come inside, traveler!
We've dancers of all
shapes and sizes!

What is this I hear of you
bathing with the locals!?

(I hear they keep her
in the castle dungeons...)

My good-for-nothing
husband spends morning
and night under Sanjo's
red lamps, the lech!

'Tis good to see a
fellow Eorzean.

If the piermaster thinks
I'm to work another
twenty-bell shift, he's as
daft as he looks!

Eight lengths.
Just as you asked, sir.

Fancy a dip down at
the springs?

Clean enough to
eat off, men!
Carry all this!? Who's going to carry me!?

Was right kind of them
to leave all this wine in
their cargo! Gahahaha!

Think we should add
another to his cart? Hahaha!

Hurry! Before the
steel cools!
A blade can never be too sharp, now.
Ten gil says there're more cubes too.
Stay focused! We're almost there!
Yaaargh! Moment of truth!

I won't break first...
I won't break first...

What kind of name is that
anyway? Eastern highland?
Make a fine rug, that one.

What are we supposed
to be aiming at again?

There!
No... Just a rabbit...
There! Over there!
No... Just a badger...

Treat a cannon like you'd
treat a woman and if you're
lucky, she won't blow your
face off. The cannon, that is.

If you people knew how
hard it was to balance
on these tails all day...

Curssses! Sssomeone's
been using my bow!
Your tailwork is pathetic!

Not a single rat in,
not a single rat out.

I suppose I could go back
to work... I also suppose I
could slay young Zenos in
a duel.

Now where in the seven
hells did he go?
Get lost! They'll find me!

A bucketful of naught,
this here is.

There's more rock here
than soil. It's a miracle
anything grows at all.

If the blight takes these,
we won't last through
the winter.

Pass me that arak, friend!
My bottle is mysteriously
empty. Hah hah hah!

Wait...
But that would mean─

Must keep the barrels
free of soot, or it'll be
our heads flying come war.

Thanking them? They
should be thanking us
for protecting their
backwood arses!

Biggest crystal east of
the Velodyna, you say?
I've seen bigger.

Iffin I find either o' yous
dockin' the dells o' any
o' these here maids, I'll
cut ye neck to crotch.

A fine spear, she is.
I cannot rightly say I've
e'er seen finer.

Papin, darling. Would you
mind fetching your ma
a skin of water?

They say the Bull tilled
this very soil by dragging
a ten-tonze boulder he
broke from Mount Yorn.

You have one mission
and one mission only─
to make it back here alive!

The mounts are
watered and fed?

Sharpened this so many
times it'll cut you if you
even look at the blade!

Sure, spinning th' fork over
me head leaves th' belly
exposed... But it looks epic!

Naught like the twang of
catgut in the morning...
or evening, for that matter.

Saw an imperial run back
this way, I did. You going
to gut 'im, <If(PlayerParameter(4))>milady<Else/>milord</If>?
But are we truly free?

Liberrraded ale's the
bestesest of ales... \\<hic>

I's thinkin' of joining
a mummer's troupe.

Are we but cattle
to be led to slaughter!?

Yeah!
...I mean, no!

All men should be
allowed a single vice.

Wouldn't want me to
mess up that pretty face
now, would you?

Whydo I e'en bother
drinkin' it if I's juss goina
leaveitall 'ere onna street?

This has been
a long time coming.

We'll need to make an
incision here...and here.

I've thinned this tonic so
many times, an ale would
work better to numb the
patients' aches.

Here's to hopin' he's
in a better place...

The moment you let your
guard down is the moment
you die. Do I make myself
clear!?

This statue's as
hard as a rock!
Come on, Biggs, you can do this...
Now, where are those mummers off hiding?

Rice, miso, sake,
revolvers, silk...wait,
revolvers?

The smell of sulphur is
strong on the wind, today.

I never grow tired of
watchin' the Lid. The
stench, now, is another
matter.

Naught amiss at
the Price...yet.
It's right under us. I can feel it!

This land has been lawfully
claimed by the Empire.
Begone or you will be...
dealt with.
You...

Do not take another step
further into the village!
You have been warned!

These will fetch quite
the price at market.

Hic...! How manyfinners am
I hollin'up? Wait! Dontellme...
Free─hic─no four! Seven!
You need some help? There's one box, and two casks. Now can we go?

You! You've got to save
us. This man... He's not
right in the head! Please!

Only way through them
doors is iffin I's carryin'
yer nob in a sack.

Da makes the best rice
balls in the village, and
I'll plug the gob of any
who'll say he don't!

Sprung a damned leak
when I took her o'er the
shoals near Sakazuki.
Most beautiful... Yes...

Your wisdom is as
bounteous as the sea.

Whose shell is it again
that I've been polishing
all day?

Open your minds...
Open your minds...
Open your minds...

Do you think she's noticed
me standing here for the
past twelve bells?

A place for every gig
and every gig in its place.

Water, water, everywhere
and all you do is drink!

My brothers aren't
going to like this...

I'm so hungry, I could
eat a horse.

Oh, and look.
They have some here...

A nice, ripe squash would
go well with that horse...

Never been that
fond of rice...

And these fish reek
of my tribe's latrine...

Though, enough pepper
in the pot, I could boil
my boot and I reckon it'd
taste fine enough.

Like to buy some milk?
Probably good and sour
by now!

You look like you could
use a basket. Or perhaps
you know someone who
could use a basket?
Baaaaaa!

You'll find none more
skilled with a morin khuur.
I'm to herd four score rutting rams with this?

Thirsty lambs... Leave
some for the tribe, now.
Right between the legs!

Lose this fight and your
place at the fire is lost!
Closer... Closer!

Too taut...
Much too taut.

Come on! One more round!
Best twenty-eight out of
fifty-five!

What am I even doing with
this thing? I wanted to
learn the spear...

Children of the dawn
let long your horns hang...♪

On the east wind rides
the whisper of the land.♪

Ten thousand three hun-
dred and sixty-eight.
Ten thousand three hun-
dred and sixty-nine.
I am the wind. I am the sky.
Let us meditate on this.

Why must we learn letters
if it is our destiny to fight?
Oh, quiet, you!
Have at me!
A finer spear I have not seen.
Baa, baa, baa!
Baa.
We must prepare for every contingency!
Those Bertha cannons of yours are bloody fast!
The Maelstrom's cannons are no less impressive, from what I have seen...
This is it, lads!

Can ye hear us, Zenos!?
Eorzea is at yer gates!

I don't see where you are
going with this, Haname.

So we're just going
to sit and wait until
the enemy attacks!?

All we do is train!
When do we fight!?
Wrong! Float like a butter- fly, sting like a bee, not the other way around!
Better! Better!
And nothing over here.

Pretend like she's not
watching me... Pretend
like she's not watching me.

My grandmother would say,
“A crooked back makes
for straighter stalks.”

Not a beast to be found...
Well, except for those
over there... And there...

I have to keep the square
clean for when my grand-
son returns from the war.

One, one, two.
One, one, two.
So what happens now?
We can fight, godsdammit!
Imperial whoresons!
We must be ready to move at a moment's notice.
Are we not men? Do we not bleed? Do we not deserve to be free!?
The plan is set...
Won't be long now.
If the fighting spreads here...
Trust in your comrades! Have faith in yourselves and mighty Rhalgr! Victory will be ours!
Sir, yes, sir!
Sir, yes, sir!
Sir, yes, sir!
Nice work, Tchakha!
The fruit of my efforts!

Can they really be
the Fist of Rhalgr?

That technique...
It couldn't be!

How tough are these
pugilists, you reckon?

I'm keener to see how
tough the monks are.

Oh, shite, the monks
ain't doing too good.

So much for the new Fist.
'Twas nothing but talk.

...And flex and shake
and bounce and...
Bloody nerves...
Aye, that'll cut 'em to the bone...
Did you see the way they ran!?
If only it were always this easy...
Seven hells! I daresay you single-handedly won us this bridge!
We're alive, we're all alive...
Ye gods, woman! Don't tell me this was your first...
The slop ready?
Hm... Could use some salt.
As it'll ever be.

Why don't you go tell
the men it's ready?

The stew's a bit bland.
Did you forget the salt?

My apologies. We used
the last this morning.

I need one of you to
give me a hand.

I just thought... Bah,
forget I asked.

“Give me a hand.” Hah!
How about giving us a hand?

Does it look like we've one
to give?

Ugh... Wh-Who are
these bastards?

\\<pant> We...we had
no answer to them...

Keep back! Any closer
and the sickness will
spread!
Why. Won't. This. Break!?

What I wouldn't give for a
nice bloody haunch of...
Your son... I'm sorry...
Aye... No better yonder...
May the elementals show us favor in our hour of need...
Matron guide my arrows, that each might strike true...
Heh heh... The Ala Mhigan Brigade is coming for you lot...
O Thal, should I fall this day, may You grant me peace everlasting...
Victory will be ours!

Time to split skulls
the Lominsan way!
No turning back!

Da says this is the
last of the rice.

What do you think
is wrong with him?

There's barely enough
there for three more nights.
How did you get up─ Oh.
●わくわくしている男の子：元帝国基地：StmBdz993
●そわそわしている老婆：元帝国基地：StmBdz993
●わくわくしている男の子：ラジアタ：StmBdz993
●そわそわしている老婆：ラジアタ：StmBdz993
●わくわくしている男の子:：アラミゴ市街地：StmBdz994
●そわそわしている老婆:：アラミゴ市街地：StmBdz994
I can't wait to see the fireworks!
Wow! It's beautiful!
Spectacular!
They certainly made a show of it this year!
This is going to be a Moonfire to remember!
Long live the Moonfire Faire!
I feel as though...I'm being watched.
Now that muscular body is bound to bear some sin.
I love you! Tell me you love me!
I... I'm sorry. It's not me, it's you. I think we should see other people.
Searching for treasure in this heat sure is tiring.
Have the fireworks started yet?
Waiting at the beach isn't as easy as it sounds.
I can barely contain myself!
I don't know which is more beautiful─these muscles or these fireworks.
You're far more beautiful than any fireworks display.
Oh, stop it.
You're far more beautiful than any f─ N-Never mind.
Just look at that ocean!
I've never had so much fun in my life!
Hehehe. I'm holding back on the freshly baked goods.
I never knew bears could be so adorable!
But what if they get loose and go on a murderous rampage!?
Have you seen the bears' new trick yet?

Nothing to report...to you.
And who are you again?

I've seen my share of
forbidden lands, but this
here is by far the worst.

Unaspected, deaspected,
over-aspected, corrupted,
luminous, demi-, and now
protean? When will it end!?
Always. <If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),12))><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),4))>Tonight<Else/>Today</If><Else/><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),17))>Today<Else/>Tonight</If></If>'s prey?

I would feast on the
succulent flesh of fish.
\\<gasp>

Loch Seld's salt'll be
the talk of the realm!

The second floor's lost,
but the cellar seems solid...

Right, let's get the
equipment cleaned up
and in working order!
Do I fight, or...?
Never in all my days...
Damn the Qalyana!
Of all the places to die...

Baut...
Save me...
I'll not fall here!

Bah, this spear
will have to do!
What in the hells!?

I came in peace!
I leave in pieces!?

We must protect
the envoys!
Accept your fate!

It's Her!
The Goddess Herself!
That was a right mess, eh?

Saved by the Butcher.
The bloody Butcher...
They disssgrace all Ananta...

My thanks.
I'd thought myself done for.

I was ill prepared
for such a meeting...
Have you a moment?
Always, my friend.

I'm to search for relics
today. Might you have a
request?

You know my tastes─
the older, the better.

You're back...and so soon.
Did fortune bless you?
She did, my friend! She did!
This is positively ancient!
Now where to put it...
Ever occupied, these ones.
Just as brilliant as yesterday.

Oh great kami, can you
hear me, your humble admirer?

This piece is so polished,
I can see the future in it!
Here's a list for next time.

Do you think our friends in
Namai will come again?
I'm the lord of all Doma!

Hien...
I've found you at last...
Ugh, my aching neck...
Ready for your next task?
Hnnngh!

Lady Yugiri!
Show us that move again!

What a mess.
We'll need more workers...
Fifteen...sixteen...

Help!
I can't hold on!

I sweep and I sweep...
Still dirt.
Another crate here for you.

Right. Put it down
with the others.
All clear on the docks!

Master Tsuranuki says
he isn't hungry.

He needs to eat.
I'll take a bowl over myself.

Now, where did...
Ugh, I've looked everywhere!
I'll get to it, then.

That smells wonderful!
What's in it?

Just tofu and vegetables!
And maybe a secret spice
or two.
I've brought you a poultice!

I told you...
...to leave me be...
Do you have enough miso?

I'll check.
Just a moment!

Miso...miso...
Which jar was it again...?

Please hurry.
I can feel my
fingers slipping...
Kill them! Kill them all!

These salt fleas will
suck the poor girl dry!

I sssee...
I shall have some more delivered.

A swarm of tracer antlions
is approaching from the north!

Then you'd better
round up some men
and take care of it!

We are eager
to prove ourssselves.

Perhaps we should
ask for something less
dangerous this time?

Surely you don't need
those cast-off skins?
Name your price!
Are you in need of provisions?

We've got enough food,
but we're running low on arak!
Understood!

A marid eats as much
in a day as five chocobos
do in a sennight.

They say the best salt's
that what's been harvested
by hand...er, rake.

They seem to be doing
just fine without my help.

You see anything, you
either kill it or you run─
just not in this direction.

I can put an arrow in the
eye of a yabby from a
hundred paces...give or
take ninety-five.

If I find you've been cutting
Master Lolorito's salt with
chalk again...
Never! You have my word!

There's plenty of salt to
sell...but no one to buy it.

These blocks are not
going to move themselves.
You've two, don't you?
I could use another hand.

If it helps Ala Mhigo,
I'll rake from dawn till dusk!

They say there is none
finer than Saltery salt,
and the Bismarck must
have the finest!

Thank Nophica for pack
chocobos. I don't fancy
carrying a sack of salt all
the way back to Gridania...

Mmm...
I don't know which
to sample first!

You can't leave without
a souvenir!
So, everything is salted...?
Aye, your father'd be proud...
It's all so busy now!

Salted fish! Salted treats!
Go on, have a taste!

Our quality is second to none!
And production has increased tenfold!

Now that the factory's up and
working, it's a matter of
expanding operations...

I'm sure we can find
work for them all...

Now we've more hands than
we know what to do with!

We didn't see nothing if
you didn't see nothing.

But we have done nothing
wrong! Nothing!
You're looking better today!

No thanks to you and
your nosiness.

Ishibushi! Help! I know you
can hear me! Ishibushi!
I can take over, if you like...
Aye, aye, that's the way...
Area past the gate's not safe.
It's not a bad idea, but...

Must you be forever ringing...
that infernal bell...
So I says to the maiko, I says...

Way's closed. We're still
clearing plots.
Rice...is happiness...
I could do this all <If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),12))><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),4))>night<Else/>day</If><Else/><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),17))>day<Else/>night</If></If>!
Ma's calling for you!
Not now! I'm busy!

Da says he's gonna throw all
your toys in the One River if
you don't come right now!
I'm not falling for that again!
Fine! See what happens!
Leave the materials here?
Aye, right there's fine!

I can't wait to see what it
looks like when it's finished!

Wonder what they're
going to do with it...
Where do you want these?
Give me a moment!

Where did I leave
that ledger...?

(Don't...don't mind
me over here... Ugh...)

Then what would you like
us to purchase instead?
That ought to suffice for now.

Looks like we've still
got plenty of spices.
Very good, very good...

Hmm... Thought we had more
around here somewhere...

I don't think we've got enough
vegetables to last the week.

Let Kozakura know.
She'll take care of it.

Everything is accounted for.
I triple-checked.

Including the materials
for Master Tsuranuki?
...Perhaps I should check again.
Perhaps you should.
I come bearing gifts!
Any luck?
I've got a good feeling...
Something took the bait!
Oho!
A marvelous catch!
Let's see what else is biting!
Reeled it in too quickly...?
Don't give up so easily!
...Is this upside down?
Need anything?

Might could do with
a few more boards!
I'll see what I can do.
Smiths need more boards─
It's time to go!
Can't we stay another night?

No! We didn't come
all the way here to
laze about!

But we might never
be able to sleep on
such comfy beds again!

I'll blame you if
someone else claims those
marks before we do!

One more night!
That's all I ask!
Kweh!

We're spreading
ourselves too thin...
Tell me, does this hurt?

Ah! Only when you
poke it like that!

That means you're
on the mend.

Be more careful in future.
You're no good to us dead.
Argh! My stomach!

You shouldn't eat
wild berries. They
could be poisonous!

Do it again, and I'll
cut you open and
dig them out myself!

I could while away the hours,
Liftin' bags of salt and flour,
If I only had a crane.♪

Winching her up, then!
Stand clear!
The buckets are full!

A manfool!
A manfool in our midst!
I hate manfools!
The manfool is still about...
Gah! What a stalker!

Haven't seen you around
before. You new?

Sure am! Just went 
through the change!

Heh, pretty rare for a rat
to live long enough─

Rat? Rat!?
I am an otter, good sir!

That's it! I'm going to
go and see the sacred
crystal right this instant!

Don't do it! Genbu's gonna
put a curse on you!
Hah! You can't scare me!
None shall pass!
Just this once! Please!

Set one hoof inside and
Genbu will curse you for
ten thousand years!

Fine! But you haven't
heard the last of this!
They wouldn't let me pass...

Of course not!
They didn't before,
so why would they now!?

It's been a while since
I said hello...

I am of a mind to hunt.
Interested?
Such serenity, such peace...
Though my body aches...

I no longer fear for my soul.
My thanks to you...
Hehe, you're funny!
Do you have any more medicine?

It's getting harder to come by.
You'll have to pay double.

Didn't think you'd come back,
given your condition...
...Was curious, is all.
Never hurts to have an extra set of eyes looking over the hull!

Need to get this
tub patched up...

Look at you, boy.
Life on the sea has
made you strong...

Mother, I...
I never thought
I'd see you again.

We hardly dared hope!
Thank the kami you're alive...

Who's your friend?
A new auspice?
Meow!♪

Oh him? He's just some
cat that wandered in.
Wandered in? Past the wards and guards and liquid hot magma!?

Is it appropriate to
grab him like that?

As long as it's above
the belt... I think...

Is that it?
I can still carry more.
I could use a dozen more like you...

That's it, my friends.
Now lift your knees higher.

You did it!
You slew the meownster!

Don't forget to carve
a scale or two off his hide.

Tell me more of how you
fractured that man's skull!
Time for a break? Yes, yes?

No Namazu may wield a
bow without supervision.

I almost made it up
onto the horse today!
Mmm, fish... Yes, yes...
Fins off the offering!
I-I was just looking!

Are you sure? Your
eyes say you are lying...
They do not! No, no.
Eat the offering one time and never hear the end of it...

Are you in need of
a target or three?
My fins hurt...

What a coincidence!
My fins hurt too!

Amazing! Mine
hurt more, though.
Will you please come down?
I c-cannot just now...
Wasshoi! Wasshoi!
No, no. Over here!
Over here! Yes, yes.
Whatever is the matter?
My happi is missing!

I know we have
extras somewhere...
Wait, are you not wearing it?
Wow! So I am!
Steady yourself!
Anything broken?
\\<puff> \\<puff>
One more...for the road!
Bit bland, isn't it...
Maybe a dash of miso...
Be careful with that miso!
What will you be selling?
You'll see!
Good, good...
This ought to suffice...
Gosh, that smells good!

And what kind of stall
are you hoping for?
A salmon stall!
Err... Just salmon?
I suppose...that might...
They look so real...
I wanna try one!
But I haven't got much─
One of each, please!
What!? Absolutely not!
...All right, one. One!
Hehe... So many choices...
All laid out, like you asked.
Oh? Where's the eggplant?
